{"tid":1587620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［全世界都反華］一帶一路國家哈薩克爆發反中國示威　57人被捕","createTime":"2019-09-22T13:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T19:14:27.000Z","uid":262146,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20835b08333ac281985a57d0bd11718a63cbf90c","tid":1587620,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMPoqim.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMPoqim.jpg&h=5145b43c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqV0RJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqV0RJ.png&h=40b0f3e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5bx25t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5bx25t.jpg&h=56a15f70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vX34Ucs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvX34Ucs.jpg&h=f7921243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中亞國家哈薩克首都努爾蘇丹、最大城市阿拉木圖及部分較細城市昨有反華示威，抗議中國對該國的影響力日漸擴大，以及首任總統納扎爾巴耶夫雖辭職仍繼續掌控國家。在努爾蘇丹和阿拉木圖共有57人被捕，而其他城市則最少有20人遭拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n在努爾蘇丹，有示威者拉起橫額「我們不要讓中國擴張」及「老人是敵人(意指扎爾巴耶夫)」，另有人高叫「釋放政治犯」。自由亞洲電台稱，一名女示威者被帶上警車前，站在警員面前高舉雙手，呼喊「我們是和平示威，雙手沒有武器」，另有一名少女遭一群警員強行拘捕，她的母親聲稱，女兒只是與妹妹去商店購物，非參加示威。在阿拉木圖，示威者不滿哈薩克與中國設立聯營公司，高叫反華及反扎爾巴耶夫口號後，被警員迅速帶走。<br />\n<br />\n中國是哈薩克最大投資者及貿易夥伴，也從哈薩克輸入原油及天燃氣，最近更計劃將部分中國工廠遷往哈薩克，引起當地人不滿。有指部分中國公司及西方公司，只聘少許當地員工，而他們的薪酬也低於外國員工。<br />\n今次示威由被禁政黨民主選擇發起，其領袖是現時流亡法國的銀行家阿布利亞佐夫(Mukhtar Ablyazov)，他遭哈薩克、俄羅斯和烏克蘭指控侵吞50億美元公款及通緝。阿布利亞佐夫一直大力抨擊納扎爾巴耶夫執政，後者雖於今年3月辭職，但仍掌控國家安全委員會及執政黨。當局指阿布利亞佐夫是政治活動激進分子，參與其發起的運動便屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【最大投資貿易夥伴】不滿中國影響力擴大-哈薩克爆反華示威-189748\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E3%80%90%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%A4%A5%E4%BC%B4%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8A%9B%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7-%E5%93%88%E8%96%A9%E5%85%8B%E7%88%86%E5%8F%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-189748&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBmqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=88bfeea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【最大投資貿易夥伴】不滿中國影響力擴大-哈薩克爆反華示威-189748</a>"},{"pid":"56bdafe3f05e218d52ba7de753dcbd271a53ff41","tid":1587620,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b2ecbab40a856790f7bf64b15c4b4eeb6e47af0","tid":1587620,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56bdafe3f05e218d52ba7de753dcbd271a53ff41","tid":1587620,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一秒"},{"pid":"f7d03f59e13a01baf128e04ad7905111896c7a9a","tid":1587620,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"真克警"},{"pid":"e6ea1767863d68f37281cb14ade4d1088059f63b","tid":1587620,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b2ecbab40a856790f7bf64b15c4b4eeb6e47af0","tid":1587620,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56bdafe3f05e218d52ba7de753dcbd271a53ff41","tid":1587620,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一秒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20